SUMMARY: Oregon Coast Film Festival
DESCRIPTION:The 100-year-old Egyptian Theatre of Coos Bay\, Oregon is see
 king short films (-20min) for our 2026 Oregon Coast Film Festival. We are
  looking for films with a connection to Oregon\, either through subject\,
  location\, cast\, and/or crew. Films may be documentary\, narrative\, st
 udent\, or any other form.\n\nThe actual festival will be held April 10-1
 2\, 2026. Please find more information on our FilmFreeway: https://filmfr
 eeway.com/oregoncoastfilmfestival
CATEGORIES:film-making,film-festivals,Oregon-short-films
