SUMMARY: You Stupid Darkness!
DESCRIPTION:In a cramped\, crumbling office\, four volunteers spend a few
  hours every Tuesday night on the phone telling strangers that everything
  is going to be okay.\n\nAs the outside world disintegrates\, they teeter
  on the edge of their own personal catastrophes. Their hopes and fears be
 come entangled as they try\, desperately\, to connect with the callers an
 d with each other.\n\nSam Steiner's You Stupid Darkness! is an urgent pla
 y about the struggle for optimism and community amid the chaos of a world
  falling apart.
