SUMMARY: Portland Winter Light Festival
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the 11th annual Portland Winter Light Festival\, 
 now entering its second decade of illuminating art and creativity.\n\nThi
 s free and inclusive event will take place from February 6 - February 14\
 , 2026\, at various locations throughout the city.\n\nEvent Highlights:\n
 \nTheme: “All The Little Things”: This year’s theme explores how the smal
 lest things can carry the greatest weight—how insects have more power whe
 n they work together. How a tiny stone can reflect light\, and how one me
 mory can set you on a path to the future.\n\nFestival Dates: February 6 -
  14\, 2026\n\n   * Anchor Sites Open: February 6 & 7and February 13 & 14 
 (Fridays and Saturdays only)\n    6 - 10 PM at Pioneer Courthouse Square\
 , World Trade Center Plaza\, and Electric Blocks.\n   * Additional major 
 installation sites include PSU\, Director Park\, Waterfront Park\, Ankeny
  Alley\, and Old Town.\n   * Glow Bar will be open\n   * Performances and
  Live Events: Times and specific locations will vary\; see the Festival w
 ebsite for details.\n   * All Other Festival Pop-Up Locations: February 6
  - 14\, 6 - 10 PM unless otherwise noted\n   * A comprehensive map with a
 ll locations and hours will be released in January.\n\nSign up for our ne
 wsletter at http://pdxwlf.com/ pdxwlf.com/join-our-newsletter/ https://pd
 xwlf.com/join-our-newsletter/ https://pdxwlf.com/join-our-newsletter/ to 
 be the first to receive notifications!\n\nAdmission: All events are free 
 and open to all ages and abilities.\n\nAccessibility: The festival venues
  are accessible to people with disabilities.\n\nContact Information:\n\nO
 rganizer: Portland Winter Light Festival\nEmail: info@pdxwlf.com mailto:i
 nfo@pdxwlf.com https://www.eventbrite.com/e/portland-winter-light-festiva
 l-10-year-anniversary-tickets-1004649572917?aff=oddtdtcreator\nWebsite: h
 ttp://www.pdxwlf.com http://www.pdxwlf.com/ www.pdxwlf.com\n\nFollow Us:\
 n\n  * Facebook: www.facebook.com/pdxwlf/ https://www.facebook.com/pdxwlf
 / https://www.facebook.com/pdxwlf/\n  * Instagram: www.instagram.com/port
 landwinterlightfestival/ https://www.instagram.com/portlandwinterlightfes
 tival/ https://www.instagram.com/portlandwinterlightfestival/\n  * Vimeo:
  vimeo.com/pdxwlf https://vimeo.com/pdxwlf https://vimeo.com/pdxwlf\n\nDo
 n’t miss this opportunity to be part of a luminous journey celebrating ov
 er a decade of creativity and wonder. Mark your calendars and invite your
  friends and family to experience the magic of the 2026 Portland Winter L
 ight Festival. We can’t wait to see you!\n\nThe Portland Winter Light Fes
 tival is a Willamette Light Brigade Event.
CATEGORIES:Festival,Outdoor,Free,Art
