SUMMARY: PSU Choirs: Bloom
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an evening of festive harmony\, heartfelt collabo
 ration\, and the timeless power of voices raised together\, featuring the
  PSU Rose\, Thorn\, Briar and University Choirs. Our graduate students wi
 ll present the work they’ve cultivated throughout their studies. Like pet
 als opening toward the sun\, this recital is a showcase of artistry in fu
 ll bloom—featuring fresh conducting voices and imaginative programming fr
 om the next generation of choral educators and leaders.
