SUMMARY: Paint Night at Tallman Brewing
DESCRIPTION:Paint & Brews at Tallman Brewing\n\nJoin us for a fun evening
  where creativity meets craft beer and Food trucks!\n\nWhether you're a s
 easoned artist or just looking to try something new\, Paint & Brews at Ta
 llman Brewing is the perfect way to unwind\, sip on some tasty brews\, an
 d create your own masterpiece. Bring your friends\, enjoy the relaxed vib
 e\, and let your artistic side flow alongside delicious drinks.\n\nThis C
 lass is perfect for couples Date Night but also great for singles. You si
 mply decide which one of the two you want to paint when you arrive the ni
 ght of! Its nice to have choices isnt it?\n\n*Ages 12+up\n\n**Please Arri
 ve early if you want to sit with your group and reserve your spots.\n\n**
 *We also recommend arriving early to order/eat from the food trucks since
  table space during the class is limited.\n\nSee you in February!
CATEGORIES:Paint-Night,Paint-Class,Brewery,Food-Trucks
