 eff Kelly’s Valentine’s Dinner features a seasonal three-course menu high
 lighting winter’s best ingredients\, with optional enhancements and curat
 ed wine pairings to elevate the evening. The Valentine’s offerings will b
 e available alongside Amaterra’s standard winter menu.\n\nHighlights incl
 ude:\n\n  * Mushroom Toast | local mushrooms\, black winter truffle\, Cas
 cadia Creamery Sawtooth cheese\, toasted brioche\n  * Ribeye | crispy pot
