 | mussels\, clams\, shrimp\, Dungeness crab\, fluke\, smoked tomato fume\
 , grilled sourdough\n  * Basque Cheesecake\n\nSpecial Valentine’s cocktai
 l features will also be available\, including the Valentino\, Clover Club
 \, and a Queen of Hearts mocktail.
