SUMMARY: Celebrate Valentine’s Day Weekend at Amaterra Winery
DESCRIPTION:Looking for a beautiful way to celebrate love this Valentine’
 s Day weekend? Amaterra Winery https://amaterrawines.com/visit/ invites c
 ouples to indulge in a romantic\, chef-driven dining experience with stun
 ning views\, live music\, and a menu designed to delight every sense.\n\n
 Chef Jami’s Valentine’s Dinner features a thoughtful five-course tasting 
 menu inspired by the season’s best ingredients. Guests are welcomed with 
 warm Japanese-style milk bread and cherry blossom butter before enjoying 
 a curated snack board and a choice of artfully prepared starters\, entrée
 s\, and desserts.\n\nHighlights include:\n\n  * Dungeness Crab & Fontina 
 Cheese Fonduta with torn focaccia\n  * Cast Iron Roasted Wagyu Beef Shoul
 der Tender with black garlic-red wine jus\n  * Flourless Dark Chocolate L
 ayer Cake with red wine-poached pears and whipped Chantilly\n\nAmaterra P
 ortland's menu is a prix fixe menu with additional a la carte options\, b
 ut they will NOT have their dinner menu available during the 2/13-15 week
 end. Vegetarian and gluten-free options are available.
CATEGORIES:Valentine's,Drinks,Dinner,Prix-Fixe
