SUMMARY: Valentine's Express Steam Train Ride
DESCRIPTION:Join us Valentine’s Day weekend on Saturday\, February 14\, a
 nd Sunday\, February 15\, for a charming ride behind a historic steam loc
 omotive. Experience the romance of vintage rail travel with your sweethea
 rt\, friends\, or family.\n\nGuests will receive a complimentary glass of
  champagne. Beer\, wine\, and non-alcoholic beverages will also be availa
 ble for purchase\, along with special sweet treats.\n\nFree admission to 
 the Center is included with your train ticket.\n\nTrain Departure Times: 
 12:00pm\, 1:30pm\, 3:00pm\, 4:30pm on Saturday and Sunday\n\nTicket Price
 s: Adult $24\, Child $17\, Senior $21.50\, Military $21.50\, Family Pass 
 (2 Adults & 2 Children) $74\n\nDon’t miss this sweet ride—book your ticke
 ts https://orhf.org/blog/valentines-express-steam-train-february-14-15-20
 26/ today!
