SUMMARY: Valentine's Day Improv Games | Dinner\, Drinks\, Flirting & Fun
DESCRIPTION:Forget the roses\, the bar-hopping\, and the endless pressure
 . Instead... join your fellow Portlanders for a fun and DELICIOUS evening
  of food\, flirting\, and joyous improvising in a supportive and welcomin
 g environment. We'll provide the food & drinks and the welcoming improv g
 ames to help you get to know one another. You bring your best self and a 
 willingness to meet others in a fun way. Join\n\nThis is one-time event a
 nd a FABULOUS opportunity to meet new friends or romantic partner in a pl
 ayful\, insightful\, and powerful way. Straight? LGBTQ+? All are welcome.
 \n\nEATZ: Delicious & healthy Mediterranean dinner for all diets included
  in the price\n\nSIPS: We'll have drinks with and without booze\, also in
 cluded in the price\n\nPLAY: unscripted games that get everyone laughing\
 n\nAGES: 25+ but\, you know: we're open\n\nSIZE: Event capped at 40 peopl
 e\n\nPARK: We've got a dozen spots available in the lot and plenty of off
  street parking available as well
CATEGORIES:Nightlife,Valentine's-Day,Improv,Dinner
