DESCRIPTION:Seattle-based jazz vocalist\, songwriter\, and commanding liv
 e performer Eugenie Jones ignites the stage in Portland on Friday\, Febru
 ary 20\, 2026\, at the Jack London Revue. The evening promises an unforge
 ttable journey through sultry\, expansive jazz\, where fiery rhythm and b
 lues collide with her velvet vocals.\n\nRenowned for her distinctive "smo
 ke & satin" vocals and electrifying stage presence\, Jones has earned int
 ernational acclaim for live performances that effortlessly weave inventiv
 e takes on vintage jazz\, soulful original compositions\, and classic R&B
 . She will be joined by an exceptional trio featuring Nick Allison (piano
 )\, Jonathan Green (bass)\, and Greg Campbell (drums)\, promising an even
 ing of unrivaled spontaneity and rhythmic vitality.
