SUMMARY: Portland Spirit River Rhythms
DESCRIPTION:On Friday nights through April\, you can enjoy the talents of
  local professional vocalists during\n\na three-course dinner cruise on t
 he Portland Spirit. Thoughtfully timed throughout the evening\,\n\ntheir 
 melodies complement beautiful springtime river views.\n\n\nDinner Cruise 
 Time: 6:00 pm – 8:30 pm\n\n\nMelissa Gale\n\nFebruary 20th & 27th | March
  6th & 13th\n\nMelissa is so excited to be here\, on the Willamette River
 \, with y’all! Theater credits\n\ninclude: The Office Holiday Party Music
 al Extravaganza (Sheila)\, Church & State\n\n(Alex)\, Evita (Eva)\, The H
 ispanic Latino/Latina/Latinx/Latine Vote (Nicola)\, Frida:\n\nUn Retablo(
 Spirit of Frida)\, Grease (Rizzo)\, All Shook Up (Ensemble)\, Peppermint\
 n\nBear Asks Witch Way To Christmas (Gert)\, Las Mujeres (Rita Hayworth).
  She\n\nstudied at New World School of the Arts in Miami\, FL and receive
 d a BFA in\n\nTheatre Performance.\n\n\nBrit Eagan\n\nMarch 20th & 27th\n
 \nBrit is a versatile performer and lifelong Oregonian excited to be sing
 ing aboard\n\nthe Portland Spirit. With a dynamic mix of jazz standards\,
  musical theatre\n\nfavorites\, and pop hits\, her set is sure to have yo
 u humming all the way home.\n\nBrit studied vocal performance at Portland
  State and Umpqua Community\n\nCollege and has performed in over 30 music
 als across the state. Local\n\naudiences may recognize her from Broadway 
 Rose Theatre Company (most\n\nrecently Frenchy in Grease and Lois in Sh-B
 oom!)\, as well as with Lakewood\n\nCenter for the Arts\, Motive Theatric
 s\, or Millennium Dance Band.\n\n\nAlyssa Birrer Oliner\n\nApril 3rd\, 10
 th\, 17th & 24th\n\nAlyssa is an Oregon native\, born in Portland and rai
 sed on the South Coast.\n\nShe has performed professionally at the Oregon
  Shakespeare Festival\, Oregon\n\nCabaret Theatre and other locations on 
 the East Coast. She has been seen locally\n\non stage at Lakewood Center 
 for the Arts\, Broadway Rose and more. Alyssa is a\n\ngreat lover of musi
 cal theatre and has been singing and performing all her life.
CATEGORIES:Livemusic,Fooddandrinks
