SUMMARY: Monster Jam® Portland
DESCRIPTION:MONSTER JAM® BRINGS FULL-THROTTLE FAMILY FUN TO MODA CENTER –
  FEBRUARY 27–MARCH 1\, 2026\n\nExperience the ultimate family motorsports
  event as Monster Jam® roars into Portland’s Moda Center for a weekend pa
 cked with heart-pounding action! Watch the world's best drivers push 12\,
 000-pound Monster Jam® trucks to the limits in adrenaline-fueled Racing\,
  2-Wheel Skills\, and Freestyle competitions that are unscripted\, unexpe
 cted\, and unforgettable.\n\nCheer on your favorites as these giant truck
 s tear up the dirt—pulling off jaw-dropping stunts and soaring through th
 e air in epic battles for the Event Championship. Fans get in on the acti
 on too\, live scoring the excitement as drivers compete for the top spot.
 \n\nDATES & TIMES\nFriday\, February 27\, 2026 – 7:00 PM\nSaturday\, Febr
 uary 28\, 2026 – 1:00 PM & 7:00 PM (Pit Party: 10:30 AM–12:00 PM)*\nSunda
 y\, March 1\, 2026 – 1:00 PM (Pit Party: 10:30 AM–12:00 PM)*\n*Pit Party 
 requires event ticket AND pit pass for entry.\n\nLOCATION\nModa Center\nO
 ne Center Court\, Suite 200\, Portland\, OR 97227\n\nTICKETS\nTickets and
  Pit Party Passes are on sale now at Ticketmaster.com https://www.ticketm
 aster.com/monster-jam-tickets/artist/1542376?venueId=123078&camefrom=CFC_
 FELD_WEBSITE and at the Moda Center box office.\n*Ticket prices subject t
 o change\; additional venue/ticketing fees may apply.\n\nArrive early for
  the Monster Jam Pit Party before Saturday and Sunday daytime shows—meet 
 drivers\, get autographs\, and snap photos with the trucks up close. Don’
 t miss the pre-show Monster Jam Trackside experience\, featuring driver i
 nterviews\, pit crew sneak peeks\, and giveaways to get fans pumped befor
 e showtime. Truck and driver lineup to be announced.\n\nFor event details
  and updates\, visit MonsterJam.com https://www.monsterjam.com/en-us/even
 ts/portland-or/feb-27-2026-mar-01-2026/ .
