 uance\, harmony\, and craftsmanship of Hibiki whisky. Each course unfolds
  alongside a curated progression of distinguished expressions\, culminati
 ng in a rare tasting of Hibiki 21 Year Old — a benchmark of Japanese blen
 ding mastery.\n\nPresented at Meadowrue’s enchanting bar\, guests experie
 nce the menu in close proximity to the culinary and bartending craft\, wi
 th storytelling and technique woven into every pour and plate. The evenin
 g offers a highly personal exploration of Japanese flavor\, seasonality\,
  and whisky artistry.\n\nReservations are limited for this exclusive thre
 e-night collaboration.\n\n
