SUMMARY: Wild Coast Film Festival
DESCRIPTION:The Wild Coast Final Festival is celebrating its 3rd year of 
 bringing wildlife and conservation films from renowned regional and inter
 national storytellers to Astoria\, OR\, highlighting stories of untamed w
 ildness and the indomitable human spirit. With film blocks spanning wildl
 ife\, adventure and science\, screenings will be held at the historic Col
 umbian Theater. Online viewing is also available.\n\nThe four days of fes
 tivities will also include: community building pop-up events and panel di
 scussions\; educational and art-focused nature walks led by award winning
  wildlife photojournalists (National Geographic\, Smithsonian\, Audubon\,
  International League of Conservation Photographers)\; showcasing of loca
 l and regional businesses and non-profits\; and\, prize raffles. Local po
 p-up events and panel discussions are informal and open to the public.\n\
