SUMMARY: Come As You Are Festival 2026
DESCRIPTION:Heidi Duckler Dance Northwest is proud to present Come As You
  Are\, an annual festival at PLACE studios on Saturday\, March 14. The in
 timate evening will provide an inside look at HDD/NW’s process of creatin
 g a major work of movement\, place\, and storytelling.\n\nHeidi Duckler w
 ill work with dancers\, Charles Roy and Daniel Giron and composer/percuss
 ionist Machado Mijiga\, creating a prologue to a new site specific work i
 nspired by John Steinbeck’s Grapes of Wrath. This piece merges music\, mo
 vement\, image and architecture in a provocative transformation of place 
 and community.\n\nGuests are invited to enjoy wine and snacks in a relaxe
 d\, salon-style environment that encourages creative conversation with th
 e artists. Come As You Are is an immersive celebration of collaboration\,
  creativity\, and the gathering of community.
CATEGORIES:festival,portland,dance,performance
