SUMMARY: Love\, Shakespeare
DESCRIPTION:Portland's favorite improvised Shakespeare troupe is attempti
 ng something new! After tackling Shakespeare's comedies and tragedies\, L
 ove\, Shakespeare will breathe new life into the Bard's least performed w
 orks: the Histories. Watch as seasoned Portland comedians attempt somethi
 ng audacious: a fully improvised Elizabethan history based on audience su
 ggestions. Each show will be an unpredictable mix of politics\, intrigue\
 , betrayal\, and succession (all with the group's signature comedic bent)
 . Follow a merry band of players – former buddies of the great Will himse
 lf – as they unravel one of Shakespeare's “unfinished” historical gems. P
 erfect for fans of Game of Thrones or Succession.
CATEGORIES:improv,comedy,theatre,shakespeare
