 his radiant resurrection\, hear storms calmed and demons cast out in vivi
 d motets. Two of Arvo Pärt’s modern masterpieces complete the program\, s
 himmering with quiet awe: timeless expressions of hope\, healing\, and tr
 anscendence. Come\, and let your spirit be moved by the miraculous singin
 g of our friends The Tallis Scholars.\n\n\nProgram\n\nRenaissance motets 
 by Giovanni Gabrieli\, Francisco Guerrero\, Jacobus Gallus\, Thomas Talli
 s\, Tomás Luis de Victoria\, and Giaches de Wert\n\nArvo Pärt (b. 1935): 
 :\nTribute to Caesar\; Virgencita Arvo Pärt: Tribute to Caesar\; Virgenci
 ta in honor of Our Lady of Guadalupe
