SUMMARY: Walking the Path
DESCRIPTION:Tickets on Sale March 2026\n\nLink: www.orsingers.org/ors/wal
 king-the-path https://www.orsingers.org/ors/walking-the-path\n\nJoin Oreg
 on Repertory Singers for Walking the Path\, an immersive concert experien
 ce\ninspired by the ancient pilgrimage of the Camino de Santiago. Anchore
 d by selections\nfrom Joby Talbot’s Path of Miracles—which left our audie
 nce breathless three years\nago—this program weaves together Medieval cha
 nts\, Renaissance gems\, and modern\nmasterworks that echo the spiritual 
 and physical journey of the Camino. With soaring\nharmonies and rich stor
 ytelling\, Walking the Path invites you to reflect\, wonder\, and\nwalk a
 longside centuries of pilgrims in search of meaning\, connection\, and\nt
 ransformation.
