SUMMARY: 3rd Annual Hearts and Hooves Gala
DESCRIPTION:Come and enjoy our 3rd Annual Gala to benefit the horses of M
 elody’s Haven of Hope where we take in horses when they needed us most an
 d live on sanctuary with us for the rest of their lives. Our aged herd de
 serves to have the best care we can give them. We invite you to join us i
 n helping the herd!\n\nIn addition\, this program connects youth with the
 se sanctuary horses. The bond created fosters a sense of self-confidence 
 and self-worth as they learn life skills caring for the herd. While worki
 ng with the horses to regain physical stamina and address medical needs i
 s a priority\, the human connection aids in healing emotional wounds for 
 these horses. This in turn affords local youth continued opportunities to
  empower themselves with these critical connections.\n\nHelp us help yout
 h and horses by buying a ticket or a table to attend the Gala\, donate an
  item or certificate for our auction\, or sponsor the evening\, a horse\,
