SUMMARY: Wine on Water
DESCRIPTION:Taste your way through Oregon on this sunset wine tasting cru
 ise aboard the Portland Spirit! More than a dozen local wineries will be 
 on board to showcase their latest vintages. Tickets include a two-hour su
 nset cruise\, 14 wine tasting tickets and a souvenir wine tasting glass.\
 n\nMay 7th\nFeatured Wineries:\n\n  * Abbey Road Farm https://abbeyroadfa
 rm.com/\n  * Amaterra Wines https://amaterrawines.com/\n  * Appassionata 
 Estate https://appassionataestate.com/\n  * Cathedral Ridge Winery https:
 //cathedralridgewinery.com/\n  * Chehalem Estate Tasting Room https://www
 .chehalemwines.com/\n  * Hip Chicks do Wine https://www.hipchicksdowine.c
 om/\n  * Jachter Family Wines https://www.jachterwine.com/\n  * Marr Cell
 ars https://marrestates.com/\n  * Patton Valley Wines https://www.pattonv
 alley.com/\n  * REX HILL https://rexhill.com/\n  * Stoller Family Estate 
 https://www.stollerfamilyestate.com/visit/\n  * Tumwater Vineyard https:/
 /www.tumwatervineyard.com/\n  * Vintyr Wine https://www.vintyrwine.com/\n
   * Yamhill Valley Vineyards https://www.yamhill.com/\n\n\nSchedule\n\n\n
 What's Included\n\n  * 2 hour sunset cruise on the Willamette River\n  * 
 Views of the Historic Milwaukie Waterfront and downtown Portland\n  * Sou
 venir stemless wine glass for tasting\n  * Fourteen (14) tasting tickets 
 each good for a 1 oz tasting — taste a wine at each winery or skip some w
 ineries and taste various wines from your favorites
CATEGORIES:Wineonwater,boozecruise,foodanddrinks
